- âœ… **Database Integration**: Consistent use of DatabaseService + methods pattern
- âœ… **Modern UX**: HTMX for dynamic updates, Alpine.js for interactivity, toast notifications
- âœ… **Type Safety**: Pydantic models for all view data structures
- âœ… **Security**: CSRF protection, input validation, path traversal prevention

